claim.claim-text:
1. A device, comprising:
a housing;
a processor operatively coupled to the housing;
a glucose monitor operatively coupled to the processor and configured to receive sensor data from a sensor control unit and generate a signal based on one or more of a fluid sample associated with an analyte concentration and the sensor data received from the sensor control unit; and
a display unit coupled to the housing and configured to output one or more information associated with the generated signal;
wherein the processor is configured to generate the information associated with the generated signal;
wherein the device enters a sleep mode if the device has not been activated for a predetermined period of time; and
wherein during the sleep mode, the device is configured to receive the sensor data from the sensor control unit and generate the signal but not output the one or more information associated with the generated signal on the display unit.

17. A device, comprising:
a housing;
a processor operatively coupled to the housing;
a glucose monitor operatively coupled to the processor and configured to receive sensor data from a sensor control unit and generate a signal associated with an analyte concentration based on the sensor data received from the sensor control unit; and
a display unit coupled to the housing and configured to output one or more information associated with the generated signal;
wherein the device enters a sleep mode if the device has not been activated for a predetermined period of time; and
wherein during the sleep mode, the device is configured to receive the sensor data from the sensor control unit and generate the signal associated with the analyte concentration based on the sensor data received from the sensor control unit but not output the one or more information associated with the generated signal on the display unit.
